to get to Bristol.

670
01:03:59.040 --> 01:04:01.000
What's in Bristol?

671
01:04:01.000 --> 01:04:02.400
My brother.

672
01:04:06.360 --> 01:04:08.720
Why isn't someone taking you there?

673
01:04:08.720 --> 01:04:12.000
