Let me see your arms.

694
01:05:22.920 --> 01:05:24.320
Good.

695
01:05:24.320 --> 01:05:25.880
All right. now. follow me.

696
01:05:27.040 --> 01:05:29.120
One. two. one. two...

697
01:05:29.120 --> 01:05:31.240
One. two...

698
01:05:32.480 --> 01:05:35.680
One. two. One. two.
