01:06:06.680 --> 01:06:08.480
So put the plant in it now.

712
01:06:13.000 --> 01:06:14.800
Watch me.

713
01:06:14.800 --> 01:06:17.040
Watch me now.

714
01:06:17.040 --> 01:06:19.400
You idiot! Come.

715
01:06:19.400 --> 01:06:21.800
Right. take one of these.

