Who else?

753
01:09:28.360 --> 01:09:30.720
Let me tell you something.
All right?

754
01:09:30.720 --> 01:09:33.960
This is my land.
So I ain't going nowhere.

755
01:09:33.960 --> 01:09:36.160
Well. the police were bound
to come knocking.

756
01:09:36.160 --> 01:09:37.920
