757
01:09:39.960 --> 01:09:42.200
Did you call them?
No.

758
01:09:43.680 --> 01:09:46.400
Listen. I know we've had our
differences.

759
01:09:46.400 --> 01:09:47.960
but I'm no snitch.

760
01:09:47.960 --> 01:09:49.840
I'm sorry about what happened.

761
01:09:53.240 --> 01:09:56.080
